    "body": "@rkapka Seems like the preset is used in the light client sync [protocol](https://github.com/ethereum/consensus-specs/blob/2c632c0087f0a692ab74987229524edbb941eeb3/specs/altair/sync-protocol.md#misc)\r\n\r\nThe beacon api https://ethereum.github.io/beacon-APIs/#/Config/getSpec says that we should include all the config constants as well as the presets\r\n> Retrieve specification configuration used on this node. The configuration should include:\r\n- Constants for all hard forks known by the beacon node, for example the phase 0 and altair values\r\n- Presets for all hard forks supplied to the beacon node, for example the phase 0 and altair values",
